&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031534929.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-35-14&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533124.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-35-47&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533800.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-36-09&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533597.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-36-33&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533473.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-36-58&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;完成后点击 Next, 选择 yes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533394.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-40-10&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;点击 Execute&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533453.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-40-46&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;完成后点击 next&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031534750.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20240103153445664&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里默认就行直接 next&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031534789.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-43-03&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择第二个&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533869.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-44-10&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;设置管理员密码 一定要记住这个密码&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533750.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-46-58&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后一路下一步就行了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里输入刚才设置的密码之后点击 check 验证然后通过 next&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533690.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-49-38&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;安装成功后会弹出两个窗口我们关闭了，来查看下 MySQL 的目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里是工具套件目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031533603.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-52-12&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里是我们安装的 MySQL 数据库目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031535512.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20240103153521470&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们可以切换到 D:\MySQL\MySQL Server8.0\bin 这个目录下执行以下 cmd&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031534739.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-58-16&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在 cmd 中输入 mysql -u root -p 然后输出刚才设置的密码就可以进入 mysql 了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202401031534708.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2022-12-03-23-59-55&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
